When love is true, sacrifice follows. When courage rises, legends are born. This Diwali, let emotions ignite the battlefield.

Experience the emotion. Feel the battle. 

Lyrics: 

Tu subah hai,
ya saba hai,
ya koi ishq ka falsafa hai.
Tu dua hai,
ya sazaa hai,
ya koi taaron ki kehkashan hai.
‚Äã

Saari dildaari teri,
yeh ishqdaari teri,
sudh-budh khoyi maine,
chadhi hai khumaari teri.
Khud se hua alag,
tujhse mila jo mere,
yaara.... yaara...
tujhse mila toh khud ko haara.
‚Äã

Ishq mein tere duniya se kya,
shaitanon se bhi lad jaaun,
bas tujhko hi main paaun.
‚Äã
Ek prem hi hai sach,
baaki sab toh yahaan pe jhootha hai re,
mujhko tujh mein mil jaana re, mil jaana re.‚Äã

Jab tak meri saans chalti,
mera har ik taana-baana tera hai... tera hai...
Roshni hai jab tak teri mere dil mein,
toh zara bhi na andhera hai... andhera hai...

‚ÄãSaans meri ruk jaaye toh bhi,
teri khushboo saath mein hogi.
Lau jali meri aankhon mein,
toh jeet apni preet ki hogi.

‚Äã
Tu subah hai,
ya saba hai,
ya koi ishq ka falsafa hai.

Music: Akshay & IP
Lyrics: IP Singh
Singers: IP Singh, Sudhir Yaduvanshi
Music Arranged & Produced: Hrishikesh Gangan, Akshay Raheja
Mix & Master: Ashwin Kulkarni

snippet.title: Predator: Badlands | Final Trailer
snippet.description:
Watch the new trailer for Predator: Badlands. Experience the film only in theaters and IMAX November 7.

Set in the future on a deadly remote planet, ‚ÄúBadlands‚Äù follows a young Predator outcast (played by newcomer Dimitrius Schuster-Koloamatangi) who finds an unlikely ally in Thia (Emmy and Golden Globe nominee Elle Fanning) as he embarks on a treacherous journey in search of the ultimate adversary. Junglee Music Tamil presents the full video of ‚ÄúThangapoovey‚Äù from the much-awaited film Madharaasi, written and directed by acclaimed filmmaker A.R. Murugadoss. Featuring the charismatic Sivakarthikeyan and the graceful Rukmini Vasanth in lead roles, this soulful track is composed by none other than Anirudh Ravichander, known for his chart-topping melodies and heart-touching compositions. Thangapoovey blends emotion with melody, capturing the essence of love and longing with poetic visuals and heartfelt lyrics.

With its mesmerizing tune and lyrical depth, Thangapoovey promises to strike a chord with music lovers and fans of Tamil cinema alike. Whether you're a follower of romantic Tamil songs or a die-hard fan of Anirudh‚Äôs music, this lyrical video is a must-watch. As anticipation builds for Madharaasi, this song sets the perfect tone, offering a glimpse into the film‚Äôs emotional landscape.
